item.title: LiKe BuTTeR: 'Predator's Mark PvP Build! (Tanky/DPS/Utility) 1.2 Builds!'
item.description:
Here is my 1.2 Predator's Mark PvP build! This build consists of 4 predator's mark, 2 final measure. Although you only have 84,000 health, you can take one HELL of a beating and still survive. The EDR helps so much against cleaners but also against explosive rounds, grenades, sticky bombs, and any other skill damage you would take. Let me know what you guys think of the build! I will be putting out a Solo 201+ build later this week! I will also be testing DPS builds as time goes on. Be sure to drop the video a LIKE if you enjoyed! Thank you!
